  "description": "Keep the celebration going with a Lake Travis wedding after party cruise! Perfect for couples and guests who aren't ready for the night to end. Private boats for 14-50+ guests with party atmosphere and late-night fun. Your wedding reception ends but the party doesn't have to! A Lake Travis after party cruise is the perfect way to extend your celebration with close friends and family. Let loose, dance, swim, and create unforgettable memories as a newly married couple. Professional crew for late-night cruises, premium sound system and disco balls for party vibes, swimming and floating under the stars (weather permitting), BYOB with cooler service, relaxed party atmosphere, continue the celebration your way, often more fun than the reception itself, perfect for the bride and groom to actually party, late-night food delivery coordination available. Fleet options: Day Tripper (intimate 14 guests, $195/hr), Me Seeks the Irony (25 guests party, $295/hr), Clever Girl (big after party 50+ guests, $495/hr). Popular timing: 10pm-1am or 11pm-2am. Packages include Ultimate Party recommended for full experience (+$250-350/hr). Book with your wedding venue date to secure availability.",
